#

Spicy Shrimp Tacos with Avocado Salsa

$15.99
500 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

shellfishfishavocado

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Tags:

seafoodtacosMexicanspicy

Description

Delicious and zesty shrimp tacos topped with creamy avocado salsa, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal!

Ingredients

  • shrimp: 1 lb
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • avocado: 1
  • lime: 2
  • cabbage: 2 cups
  • red onion: 1
  • cilantro: 1/2 cup
  • chili powder: 1 tbsp
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
